python
import tkinter as tk
from tkinter import ttk, messagebox
import sqlite3
from datetime import datetime
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# ---------- Module 1: Storage & Data Management ----------
def create_database():
    conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute('''
        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS expenses (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            date TEXT,
            category TEXT,
            amount REAL,
            description TEXT
        )
    ''')
    conn.commit()
    conn.close()

def add_expense(date, category, amount, description):
    conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("INSERT INTO expenses (date, category, amount, description) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)",
              (date, category, amount, description))
    conn.commit()
    conn.close()

def get_all_expenses():
    conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("SELECT date, category, amount FROM expenses")
    data = c.fetchall()
    conn.close()
    return data

# ---------- Module 2: Budget Entry ----------
def submit_expense():
    date = date_entry.get()
    category = category_entry.get()
    amount = amount_entry.get()
    description = description_entry.get()

    if not (date and category and amount):
        messagebox.showwarning("Input Error", "Please fill all required fields.")
        return

    try:
        amount = float(amount)
    except ValueError:
        messagebox.showerror("Invalid Input", "Amount must be a number.")
        return

    add_expense(date, category, amount, description)
    messagebox.showinfo("Success", "Expense added successfully!")
    date_entry.delete(0, tk.END)
    category_entry.delete(0, tk.END)
    amount_entry.delete(0, tk.END)
    description_entry.delete(0, tk.END)

# ---------- Module 3: Charts & Reports ----------
def show_charts():
    data = get_all_expenses()
    categories = {}
    for row in data:
        _, category, amount = row
        categories[category] = categories.get(category, 0) + amount

    if not categories:
        messagebox.showinfo("No Data", "No expense data to show.")
        return

    # Pie Chart
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.title("Expenses by Category")
    plt.pie(categories.values(), labels=categories.keys(), autopct='%1.1f%%')
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

# ---------- Main UI ----------
create_database()

app = tk.Tk()
app.title("Personal Expense Tracker")
app.geometry("400x400")

# Title
tk.Label(app, text="Enter Expense Details", font=("Helvetica", 14, "bold")).pack(pady=10)

# Date
tk.Label(app, text="Date (YYYY-MM-DD):").pack()
date_entry = tk.Entry(app)
date_entry.insert(0, datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d"))
date_entry.pack()

# Category
tk.Label(app, text="Category:").pack()
category_entry = tk.Entry(app)
category_entry.pack()

# Amount
tk.Label(app, text="Amount:").pack()
amount_entry = tk.Entry(app)
amount_entry.pack()

# Description
tk.Label(app, text="Description (optional):").pack()
description_entry = tk.Entry(app)
description_entry.pack()

# Submit Button
tk.Button(app, text="Add Expense", command=submit_expense, bg="green", fg="white").pack(pady=10)

# Show Chart Button
tk.Button(app, text="Show Charts", command=show_charts, bg="blue", fg="white").pack()

# Run the App
app.mainloop()

python
from flask import Flask, render_template, request, redirect, url_for
import sqlite3
from datetime import datetime
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import os

app = Flask(__name__)

# Database setup
def init_db():
    conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute('''
        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS expenses (
            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
            date TEXT,
            category TEXT,
            amount REAL,
            description TEXT
        )
    ''')
    conn.commit()
    conn.close()

init_db()

@app.route('/', methods=['GET', 'POST'])
def index():
    if request.method == 'POST':
        date = request.form['date']
        category = request.form['category']
        amount = float(request.form['amount'])
        description = request.form['description']

        conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
        c = conn.cursor()
        c.execute("INSERT INTO expenses (date, category, amount, description) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)",
                  (date, category, amount, description))
        conn.commit()
        conn.close()
        return redirect(url_for('index'))

    return render_template('index.html', today=datetime.today().strftime('%Y-%m-%d'))

@app.route('/report')
def report():
    conn = sqlite3.connect("expenses.db")
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("SELECT category, SUM(amount) FROM expenses GROUP BY category")
    data = c.fetchall()
    conn.close()

    if data:
        categories = [row[0] for row in data]
        amounts = [row[1] for row in data]

        plt.figure(figsize=(6,6))
        plt.pie(amounts, labels=categories, autopct='%1.1f%%')
        plt.title('Expense Distribution by Category')
        plt.tight_layout()

        chart_path = os.path.join('static', 'chart.png')
        plt.savefig(chart_path)
        plt.close()
    else:
        chart_path = None

    return render_template('report.html', chart_path=chart_path)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(debug=True)

python
from flask import Flask, render_template_string, request, jsonify
import sqlite3
from datetime import datetime
from collections import defaultdict

app = Flask(__name__)

# Initialize database
def init_db():
    conn = sqlite3.connect('expenses.db')
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute('''CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS expenses (
        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
        name TEXT,
        amount REAL,
        date TEXT,
        category TEXT
    )''')
    conn.commit()
    conn.close()

init_db()

@app.route('/')
def index():
    with open("index.html", "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        return render_template_string(f.read())

@app.route('/add', methods=['POST'])
def add_expense():
    name = request.form['name']
    amount = float(request.form['amount'])
    date = request.form['date']
    category = request.form['customCategory'] if request.form['category'] == 'Other' else request.form['category']

    conn = sqlite3.connect('expenses.db')
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("INSERT INTO expenses (name, amount, date, category) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)",
              (name, amount, date, category))
    conn.commit()
    conn.close()
    return '<script>window.location.href="/";</script>'

@app.route('/summary')
def summary():
    conn = sqlite3.connect('expenses.db')
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("SELECT name, amount, date, category FROM expenses ORDER BY date DESC")
    rows = c.fetchall()
    conn.close()

    html = "<table border='1' cellpadding='8'><tr><th>Name</th><th>Amount</th><th>Date</th><th>Category</th></tr>"
    for row in rows:
        html += f"<tr><td>{row[0]}</td><td>â‚¹{row[1]:.2f}</td><td>{row[2]}</td><td>{row[3]}</td></tr>"
    html += "</table>"
    return html

@app.route('/average')
def average():
    conn = sqlite3.connect('expenses.db')
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("SELECT name, AVG(amount) FROM expenses GROUP BY name")
    rows = c.fetchall()
    conn.close()

    html = "<table border='1' cellpadding='8'><tr><th>User</th><th>Average Expense (INR)</th></tr>"
    for row in rows:
        html += f"<tr><td>{row[0]}</td><td>â‚¹{row[1]:.2f}</td></tr>"
    html += "</table>"
    return html

@app.route('/chart-data')
def chart_data():
    conn = sqlite3.connect('expenses.db')
    c = conn.cursor()
    c.execute("SELECT category, SUM(amount) FROM expenses GROUP BY category")
    data = c.fetchall()
    conn.close()

    labels = [row[0] for row in data]
    amounts = [row[1] for row in data]
    return jsonify({"labels": labels, "amounts": amounts})

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(debug=True)

    let expenses = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("expenses")) || [];

    function toggleCustomCategory() {
      const select = document.getElementById("category");
      const customInput = document.getElementById("customCategory");
      customInput.style.display = select.value === "Other" ? "block" : "none";
    }

    function addExpense() {
      const name = document.getElementById("name").value.trim();
      const amount = parseFloat(document.getElementById("amount").value);
      const date = document.getElementById("date").value;
      let category = document.getElementById("category").value;
      const customCategory = document.getElementById("customCategory").value.trim();

      if (category === "Other" && customCategory !== "") {
        category = customCategory;
      }

      if (!name || !amount || !date || !category) {
        alert("Please fill all fields");
        return;
      }

      expenses.push({ name, amount, date, category });
      localStorage.setItem("expenses", JSON.stringify(expenses));
      document.getElementById("name").value = "";
      document.getElementById("amount").value = "";
      document.getElementById("date").value = "";
      document.getElementById("customCategory").value = "";
      document.getElementById("category").value = "Food";
      updateDisplay();
    }

    function updateDisplay() {
      // Summary Table
      let summaryHTML = "<table><tr><th>Name</th><th>Amount (â‚¹)</th><th>Date</th><th>Category</th></tr>";
      expenses.forEach(e => {
        summaryHTML += `<tr><td>${e.name}</td><td>â‚¹${e.amount}</td><td>${e.date}</td><td>${e.category}</td></tr>`;
      });
      summaryHTML += "</table>";
      document.getElementById("summaryTable").innerHTML = summaryHTML;

      // Average Table
      const userSums = {};
      const userCounts = {};
      expenses.forEach(e => {
        if (!userSums[e.name]) {
          userSums[e.name] = 0;
          userCounts[e.name] = 0;
        }
        userSums[e.name] += e.amount;
        userCounts[e.name] += 1;
      });
      let avgHTML = "<table><tr><th>Name</th><th>Average Expense (â‚¹)</th></tr>";
      for (let user in userSums) {
        avgHTML += `<tr><td>${user}</td><td>â‚¹${(userSums[user] / userCounts[user]).toFixed(2)}</td></tr>`;
      }
      avgHTML += "</table>";
      document.getElementById("averageTable").innerHTML = avgHTML;

      // Chart
      const categorySums = {};
      expenses.forEach(e => {
        categorySums[e.category] = (categorySums[e.category] || 0) + e.amount;
      });
      const labels = Object.keys(categorySums);
      const data = Object.values(categorySums);

      const ctx = document.getElementById("expenseChart").getContext("2d");
      if (window.myChart) window.myChart.destroy();
      window.myChart = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: "pie",
        data: {
          labels: labels,
          datasets: [{
            data: data,
            backgroundColor: ['#f39c12', '#3498db', '#2ecc71', '#e74c3c', '#9b59b6']
          }]
        }
      });
    }

    // Initial Load
    updateDisplay();
  </script>

      const date = document.getElementById("date").value;
      let category = document.getElementById("category").value;
      const customCategory = document.getElementById("customCategory").value.trim();

      if (category === "Other" && customCategory !== "") {
        category = customCategory;
      }

      if (!name || !amount || !date || !category) {
        alert("Please fill all fields");
        return;
      }

      expenses.push({ name, amount, date, category });
      localStorage.setItem("expenses", JSON.stringify(expenses));
      document.getElementById("name").value = "";
      document.getElementById("amount").value = "";
      document.getElementById("date").value = "";
      document.getElementById("customCategory").value = "";
      document.getElementById("category").value = "Food";
      updateUserDropdown();
    }

    function clearExpenses() {
      if (confirm("Are you sure you want to delete all expenses?")) {
        expenses = [];
        localStorage.removeItem("expenses");
        updateUserDropdown();
        clearUserView();
      }
    }

    function updateUserDropdown() {
      const select = document.getElementById("userSelect");
      const users = [...new Set(expenses.map(e => e.name))];
      select.innerHTML = `<option value="">-- Select User --</option>`;
      users.forEach(user => {
        select.innerHTML += `<option value="${user}">${user}</option>`;
      });
    }

    function updateUserView() {
      const user = document.getElementById("userSelect").value;
      if (!user) {
        clearUserView();
        return;
      }

      const userExpenses = expenses.filter(e => e.name === user);

      // Summary
      let summaryHTML = "<table><tr><th>Amount (â‚¹)</th><th>Date</th><th>Category</th></tr>";
      userExpenses.forEach(e => {
        summaryHTML += `<tr><td>â‚¹${e.amount}</td><td>${e.date}</td><td>${e.category}</td></tr>`;
      });
      summaryHTML += "</table>";
      document.getElementById("userSummary").innerHTML = summaryHTML;

      // Average
      const avg = userExpenses.reduce((sum, e) => sum + e.amount, 0) / userExpenses.length;
      document.getElementById("userAverage").innerHTML = `<p>â‚¹${avg.toFixed(2)}</p>`;

      // Chart
      const catSums = {};
      userExpenses.forEach(e => {
        catSums[e.category] = (catSums[e.category] || 0) + e.amount;
      });
      const labels = Object.keys(catSums);
      const data = Object.values(catSums);
      const ctx = document.getElementById("userChart").getContext("2d");
      if (window.userChartObj) window.userChartObj.destroy();
      window.userChartObj = new Chart(ctx, {
        type: "doughnut",
        data: {
          labels: labels,
          datasets: [{
            data: data,
            backgroundColor: ["#f39c12", "#3498db", "#2ecc71", "#9b59b6", "#e74c3c"]
          }]
        }
      });
    }

    function clearUserView() {
      document.getElementById("userSummary").innerHTML = "";
      document.getElementById("userAverage").innerHTML = "";
      if (window.userChartObj) window.userChartObj.destroy();
    }

    function showSection(id) {
      document.querySelectorAll(".section").forEach(sec => sec.classList.remove("active"));
      document.getElementById(id).classList.add("active");
      if (id === "userView") updateUserDropdown();
    }

    // Initialize on load
    updateUserDropdown();
  </script>
